---
import Layout from "../../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import {
  ThumbsUp,
  MessageSquare,
  Copy,
  ExternalLink,
  TriangleAlert,
  Layers,
  Server,
} from "@lucide/astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Blog Tech - Introduccion Docker"
  description="Introduccion a Docker para principiantes."
>
  <section
    class="font-sans antialiased min-h-screen relative overflow-x-hidden selection:bg-purple-200 selection:text-purple-900 bg-[#f8f9fa] pb-24"
  >
    <div class="relative z-10 w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 md:py-16">
      <div
        class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden"
      >
        <div
          class="bg-gray-50 border-b border-gray-100 px-4 py-3 flex items-center gap-4"
        >
          <div class="flex gap-2">
            <div
              class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[#FF5F56] border border-[#E0443E]"
            >
            </div>
            <div
              class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[#FFBD2E] border border-[#DEA123]"
            >
            </div>
            <div
              class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[#27C93F] border border-[#1AAB29]"
            >
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="font-mono text-xs text-gray-400 select-none">
            flujo-docker.mdx
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-8 md:p-16">
          <div class="font-mono text-sm mb-8 space-y-2">
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span class="text-[#e11d48] font-bold">const</span>
              <span class="text-[#475569]">ultimaActualizacion</span>
              <span class="text-gray-400">=</span>
              <span class="text-[#64748b]">'2024-05-20'</span><span
                class="text-gray-400">;</span
              >
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span class="text-[#e11d48] font-bold">const</span>
              <span class="text-[#475569]">tiempoLectura</span>
              <span class="text-gray-400">=</span>
              <span class="text-[#64748b]">'8 min'</span><span
                class="text-gray-400">;</span
              >
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span class="text-[#e11d48] font-bold">const</span>
              <span class="text-[#475569]">etiquetas</span>
              <span class="text-gray-400">=</span>
              <span class="text-gray-800">[</span>
              <span class="text-[#64748b]">"DevOps"</span><span
                class="text-gray-400">,</span
              >
              <span class="text-[#64748b]">"Contenedores"</span><span
                class="text-gray-400">,</span
              >
              <span class="text-[#64748b]">"Arquitectura"</span>
              <span class="text-gray-800">]</span><span class="text-gray-400"
                >;</span
              >
            </div>
          </div>
          <header class="mb-12">
            <h1
              class="font-mono font-bold text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-gray-900 tracking-tight leading-tight"
            >
              <span class="text-[#A755F7]">{`{`}</span>
              Dockeriza tu <br class="hidden md:block" />
              Flujo de Trabajo
              <span class="text-[#A755F7]">{`}`}</span>
              <span
                class="block text-2xl md:text-3xl mt-4 text-gray-400 font-normal"
                >: De Monolitos a Contenedores Escalables</span
              >
            </h1>
            <div
              class="mt-8 font-mono text-gray-500 text-sm md:text-base pl-2 border-l-2 border-[#ec4899]/50"
            >
              <span class="text-[#ec4899] font-bold">01</span> La consistencia es
              la clave de la escalabilidad.
            </div>
          </header>
          <article
            class="prose prose-slate prose-lg max-w-none prose-headings:font-mono prose-p:font-sans"
          >
            <p class="lead text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 font-light">
              Elimina las discrepancias de entorno. Aprende a crear contenedores
              inmutables y portátiles que garantizan la consistencia total desde
              desarrollo hasta producción.
            </p>
            <div
              class="bg-gray-50/50 border border-gray-100 rounded-lg p-6 mb-12 not-prose"
            >
              <h4
                class="font-mono text-xs font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4"
              >
                ÍNDICE
              </h4>
              <ol class="font-mono text-sm space-y-2 text-gray-600">
                <li class="flex gap-2">
                  <span class="text-[#ec4899]">1.</span>
                  <span>El Contexto</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex gap-2">
                  <span class="text-[#ec4899]">2.</span>
                  <span>Implementación Paso a Paso</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex gap-2">
                  <span class="text-[#ec4899]">3.</span>
                  <span>Datos de Validación</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex gap-2">
                  <span class="text-[#ec4899]">4.</span>
                  <span>Conclusión</span>
                </li>
              </ol>
            </div>
            <h2
              class="text-2xl font-bold mt-16 mb-6 font-mono text-gray-400 syntax-highlight-h2"
            >
              El Problema
            </h2>
            <p>
              Gestionar dependencias en diferentes entornos es un caos manual
              propenso a errores. Tienes Node 14 localmente, Node 18 en staging
              y quién-sabe-qué en producción. Depurar estas discrepancias de
              entorno drena horas de productividad cada semana.
            </p>
            <h2
              class="text-2xl font-bold mt-16 mb-6 font-mono text-gray-400 syntax-highlight-h2"
            >
              La Estrategia: Inmutabilidad
            </h2>
            <p>
              Para resolver este caos, dejaremos de tratar nuestros servidores
              como mascotas y pasaremos a usar contenedores inmutables. Aquí es
              donde entra Docker: encapsulando todo —código, tiempo de ejecución
              y herramientas— en una Imagen única.
            </p>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-16 mb-6 font-mono text-gray-900">
              Implementación Paso a Paso
            </h2>
            <p>
              Veamos cómo definimos este entorno en código. Usamos un <code
                >Dockerfile</code
              > para actuar como la receta del entorno de nuestra aplicación.
            </p>
            <div
              class="my-10 font-mono text-sm not-prose rounded-lg overflow-hidden border border-gray-200 shadow-sm bg-gray-50"
            >
              <div
                class="bg-gray-100 px-4 py-2 text-xs text-gray-500 border-b border-gray-200 flex justify-between items-center"
              >
                <span>Dockerfile</span>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                  <span class="text-gray-400 hidden sm:inline"
                    >[Solo Lectura]</span
                  >
                  <button
                    class="flex items-center gap-1.5 px-2 py-1 rounded hover:bg-gray-200/60 text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors group cursor-pointer"
                    title="Copiar código"
                  >
                    <Copy size={15} />
                    <span class="font-medium">Copiar</span>
                  </button>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="p-4 overflow-x-auto text-gray-700">
                <pre
                  class="bg-transparent border-0 p-0 m-0 text-sm font-mono"><code><span class="text-gray-400"># Comenzar con una imagen base ligera</span>
<span class="text-purple-600">FROM</span> node:18-alpine
<span class="text-gray-400"># Establecer directorio de trabajo dentro del contenedor</span>
<span class="text-purple-600">WORKDIR</span> /app
<span class="text-gray-400"># Copiar definiciones de paquetes primero para mejor caché</span>
<span class="text-purple-600">COPY</span> package*.json ./
<span class="text-gray-400"># Instalar dependencias</span>
<span class="text-purple-600">RUN</span> npm install --production
<span class="text-gray-400"># Copiar el resto del código de la aplicación</span>
<span class="text-purple-600">COPY</span> . .
<span class="text-gray-400"># Definir el comando para ejecutar la app</span>
<span class="text-purple-600">CMD</span> [<span class="text-[#64748b]">"node"</span>, <span class="text-[#64748b]">"server.js"</span>]</code></pre>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div
              class="not-prose bg-amber-50 border-l-4 border-amber-400 p-4 my-8 rounded-r-lg flex items-start gap-4"
            >
              <TriangleAlert size={40} color="#f59e0b" />
              <div>
                <h5
                  class="font-bold text-amber-800 text-sm font-mono uppercase tracking-wide"
                >
                  CONSEJO PRO
                </h5>
                <p class="text-amber-700 text-sm mt-1">
                  Usa <code
                    class="bg-amber-100 text-amber-900 px-1 py-0.5 rounded"
                    >.dockerignore</code
                  > para mantener tus imágenes ligeras y seguras. Excluir <code
                    >node_modules</code
                  > y archivos <code>.env</code> previene el bloat y la fuga de secretos.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-16 mb-6 font-mono text-gray-900">
              Validación: VM Local vs Contenedor Docker
            </h2>
            <p>
              ¿Por qué cambiar de Máquinas Virtuales? Las ganancias de
              eficiencia son masivas cuando eliminas la sobrecarga de un Sistema
              Operativo Huésped completo.
            </p>
            <div class="not-prose my-10 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              <div
                class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 flex flex-col items-center text-center"
              >
                <div
                  class="w-12 h-12 bg-gray-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4"
                >
                  <Server size={25} />
                </div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">VM Local</h4>
                <div class="w-full space-y-3 mt-4">
                  <div
                    class="flex justify-between text-sm border-b border-gray-100 pb-2"
                  >
                    <span class="text-gray-500">Tiempo de inicio</span>
                    <span class="font-mono text-red-500">~2 mins</span>
                  </div>
                  <div
                    class="flex justify-between text-sm border-b border-gray-100 pb-2"
                  >
                    <span class="text-gray-500">Tamaño</span>
                    <span class="font-mono text-red-500">~2 GB</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex justify-between text-sm">
                    <span class="text-gray-500">Aislamiento</span>
                    <span class="font-mono text-gray-700">Nivel Hardware</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div
                class="bg-purple-50/50 border border-purple-200 rounded-lg p-6 flex flex-col items-center text-center relative overflow-hidden"
              >
                <div
                  class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-16 h-16 bg-linear-to-br from-[#ec4899]/20 to-transparent rounded-bl-full -mr-4 -mt-4"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                  class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4"
                >
                  <Layers size={25} />
                </div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-purple-900 mb-2">
                  Contenedor Docker
                </h4>
                <div class="w-full space-y-3 mt-4">
                  <div
                    class="flex justify-between text-sm border-b border-purple-100 pb-2"
                  >
                    <span class="text-gray-500">Tiempo de inicio</span>
                    <span class="font-mono text-emerald-600 font-bold"
                      >~500ms</span
                    >
                  </div>
                  <div
                    class="flex justify-between text-sm border-b border-purple-100 pb-2"
                  >
                    <span class="text-gray-500">Tamaño</span>
                    <span class="font-mono text-emerald-600 font-bold"
                      >~150 MB</span
                    >
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex justify-between text-sm">
                    <span class="text-gray-500">Aislamiento</span>
                    <span class="font-mono text-gray-700">Nivel Proceso</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-dashed border-gray-200">
              <h3
                class="text-xl font-bold font-mono mb-4 text-gray-900 flex items-center gap-2"
              >
                <span class="text-[#ec4899]">function</span> conclusion()
              </h3>
              <p>
                La contenerización es la base del DevOps moderno. Al dominar el
                Dockerfile, aseguras que tu aplicación sea portátil, escalable y
                predecible.
              </p>
            </div>
          </article>
          <div
            class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-gray-100 font-mono text-sm text-gray-500"
          >
            <div
              class="mb-10 flex flex-wrap gap-8 items-center justify-between"
            >
              <div class="flex gap-6">
                <span
                  class="flex items-center gap-2 hover:text-[#ec4899] cursor-pointer transition-colors group"
                >
                  <ThumbsUp size={17} />
                  128 Me Gusta
                </span>
                <span
                  class="flex items-center gap-2 hover:text-[#ec4899] cursor-pointer transition-colors group"
                >
                  <MessageSquare size={17} />
                  32 Comentarios
                </span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex gap-4">
                <a
                  class="flex items-center gap-2 hover:text-[#ec4899] cursor-pointer transition-colors text-gray-600 text-xs"
                  href="#"
                >
                  Kubernetes 101 <ExternalLink size={17} />
                </a>
                <a
                  class="flex items-center gap-2 hover:text-[#ec4899] cursor-pointer transition-colors text-gray-600 text-xs"
                  href="#"
                >
                  Pipelines de CI/CD <ExternalLink size={17} />
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div
              class="mb-16 p-6 md:p-8 bg-gray-50/80 border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center md:items-start gap-6 text-center md:text-left"
            >
              <div class="relative shrink-0">
                <img
                  alt="Juan Pérez"
                  class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full border-4 border-white shadow-sm object-cover grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-300"
                  src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuA_RvCM9ydhCNEZDYaGS4oTnSBu-yT50j2AHmSu41RT33R9H8LmxzVyvv3onIq1eD_bW6N4Zik5GaQEfnUXZbyAKMMTV51e8G6NExsR9599Vgrsb-aSpJe9R880Ol-Hm1i3aQxKW9l4pn1vpOUuzjYkPmsjyRm_wAljquW7Hhs1ZtbLqv1XuVeg_0LDe9L3br2eoUaoo-zG5L04d0TDNCz5rrjP36aLYbmIJbl__Bep-CgO_d0dOhVu9SERkKRJwgeoVH6KZo0f1cY"
                />
                <div
                  class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-5 h-5 bg-green-500 border-2 border-white rounded-full"
                >
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col justify-center">
                <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-lg font-sans">
                  Juan Pérez
                </h3>
                <p
                  class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mt-2 mb-4 font-sans max-w-xl"
                >
                  Escrito por Juan Pérez, desarrollador Full Stack apasionado
                  por NestJS y Angular.
                </p>
                <div
                  class="flex items-center justify-center md:justify-start gap-5"
                >
                  <a
                    aria-label="Github"
                    class="text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors"
                    href="#"
                  >
                    <svg
                      class="w-5 h-5 fill-current"
                      viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                      ><path
                        d="M12 0C5.37 0 0 5.373 0 12c0 5.303 3.438 9.8 8.205 11.385.6.113.82-.258.82-.577 0-.285-.01-1.04-.015-2.04-3.338.724-4.042-1.61-4.042-1.61-.546-1.387-1.333-1.756-1.333-1.756-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.838 1.236 1.838 1.236 1.07 1.835 2.809 1.305 3.495.998.108-.776.42-1.305.763-1.605-2.665-.3-5.466-1.332-5.466-5.93 0-1.31.465-2.38 1.235-3.22-.135-.303-.54-1.523.105-3.176 0 0 1.005-.322 3.3 1.23.96-.267 1.98-.399 3-.405 1.02.006 2.04.138 3 .405 2.28-1.552 3.285-1.23 3.285-1.23.645 1.653.24 2.873.12 3.176.765.84 1.23 1.91 1.23 3.22 0 4.61-2.805 5.625-5.475 5.92.42.36.81 1.096.81 2.22 0 1.606-.015 2.896-.015 3.286 0 .315.21.69.825.57C20.565 21.795 24 17.3 24 12c0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12"
                      ></path></svg
                    >
                  </a>
                  <a
                    aria-label="X (Twitter)"
                    class="text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors"
                    href="#"
                  >
                    <svg
                      class="w-5 h-5 fill-current"
                      viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                      ><path
                        d="M18.901 1.153h3.68l-8.04 9.19L24 22.846h-7.406l-5.8-7.584-6.638 7.584H.474l8.6-9.83L0 1.154h7.594l5.243 6.932ZM17.61 20.644h2.039L6.486 3.24H4.298Z"
                      ></path></svg
                    >
                  </a>
                  <a
                    aria-label="LinkedIn"
                    class="text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors"
                    href="#"
                  >
                    <svg
                      class="w-5 h-5 fill-current"
                      viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                      ><path
                        d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433c-1.144 0-2.063-.926-2.063-2.065 0-1.138.92-2.063 2.063-2.063 1.14 0 2.064.925 2.064 2.063 0 1.139-.925 2.065-2.064 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"
                      ></path></svg
                    >
                  </a>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
